CREATE TABLE compliance_documents (
  document_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  document_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  regulation_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (regulation_id) REFERENCES compliance_regulations(regulation_id)
);

  issue_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  issue_description TEXT NOT NULL,
  document_id INT,

CREATE TABLE audit_logs (id INT PRIMARY KEY, event_time TIMESTAMP, user_id INT, event_description TEXT);

CREATE TABLE compliance_policies (policy_id INT PRIMARY KEY, policy_name TEXT, description TEXT);</t><stat>SELECT AVG(user_id) FROM user_profiles WHERE user_id > 500;</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE compliance_reports (report_id INT PRIMARY KEY, report_date DATE, policy_id INT, user_id INT);
